### Teste de Endpoints - Helpdesk API
### Roteiro de Validação Manual

### 1. GET /health - Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000/health

### 2. GET /users - Listar todos os usuários
GET http://localhost:3000/users

### 3. GET /tickets/summary - Resumo de tickets
GET http://localhost:3000/tickets/summary

### 4. GET /tickets - Listar tickets com filtros
GET http://localhost:3000/tickets

### 4.1 GET /tickets - Filtro por status
GET http://localhost:3000/tickets?status=open

### 4.2 GET /tickets - Filtro por categoria
GET http://localhost:3000/tickets?category=infra

### 4.3 GET /tickets - Busca por texto
GET http://localhost:3000/tickets?search=urgente

### 5. POST /tickets - Criar ticket
POST http://localhost:3000/tickets
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Servidor down",
  "description": "O servidor de produção está offline e urgente",
  "category": "infra",
  "requesterId": "user_1735689600000_1234"
}

### 6. GET /tickets/:id - Obter detalhes do ticket
GET http://localhost:3000/tickets/ticket_1735689600000_1234

### 7. PATCH /tickets/:id/status - Atualizar status do ticket
PATCH http://localhost:3000/tickets/ticket_1735689600000_1234/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "in_progress",
  "comment": "Começando a investigar o problema",
  "authorId": "user_1735689600000_1234"
}

### 8. PATCH /tickets/:id/status - Fechar ticket com comentário obrigatório
PATCH http://localhost:3000/tickets/ticket_1735689600000_1234/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "closed",
  "comment": "Problema resolvido. Servidor reiniciado.",
  "authorId": "user_1735689600000_1234"
}

### 9. POST /tickets/:id/comments - Adicionar comentário
POST http://localhost:3000/tickets/ticket_1735689600000_1234/comments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Adicionando mais detalhes sobre a solução",
  "authorId": "user_1735689600000_1234"
}

### 10. Testes de Erro - GET /tickets/:id com ID inválido
GET http://localhost:3000/tickets/invalid_id

### 11. Testes de Erro - POST /tickets sem campos obrigatórios
POST http://localhost:3000/tickets
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Ticket incompleto"
}

### 12. Testes de Erro - PATCH /tickets/:id/status com status inválido
PATCH http://localhost:3000/tickets/ticket_1735689600000_1234/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "invalid_status",
  "comment": "teste"
}

### 13. Testes de Erro - PATCH /tickets/:id/status fechar sem comentário
PATCH http://localhost:3000/tickets/ticket_1735689600000_1234/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "closed"
}

### 14. Testes de Erro - POST /tickets/:id/comments sem campos obrigatórios
POST http://localhost:3000/tickets/ticket_1735689600000_1234/comments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Apenas mensagem sem autor"
}

